snippet.title: Travel Guide: Things to Do in Rome! (Italy)
snippet.description:
Rome was AMAZING! From the grand Colosseum to the grounds of the Vatican (and more!) come with me as I bring to you the top things to do AND see in this ancient 'eternal city' in Italy!
💎 Get exclusive perks, postcards & gift packs here: https://link.iamaileen.tv/sub

Sending love and thanks to Through Eternity Tours for this amazing 2-Day VIP experience of Rome!

⚠️ Subscribe and stay updated on any NEW video upload: http://iAmAileen.TV  

---
[ T R A V E L - G U I D E ]
▸ Read my detailed blog report for this here: http://iamaileen.com/rome-vatican-things-to-do-2-day-tour-through-eternity-italy/

---
[ F O L L O W ]
Did you enjoy this video? Come check my travel blog!
▸ http://iAmAileen.com

You can also find me on...
▸ Facebook: http://facebook.com/iamaileencom
▸ Twitter: http://twitter.com/iamaileen
▸ Instagram & Instagram Stories: http://instagram.com/i_am_aileen

---
[ V I D E O ]
▸ Background Music: All tracks from ProleteR at https://soundcloud.com/proleter-beatmaker
▸ Camera & Video Recording Gear: https://iamaileen.com/shop/
▸ Editing Software: Final Cut Pro (Apple)

---
[ A B O U T ]
I am Aileen Adalid. At 21, I quit my corporate job in the Philippines to travel the world. Today, I am a digital nomad and entrepreneur living a sustainable travel lifestyle.

My mission? To show you how it is absolutely possible to create a life of travel, and I will help you achieve that through my detailed travel guides, resources, and tips. But above all, I hope that my story and my videos will inspire you to go after your travel dreams!

So come with me on this crazy journey as I bring the world to you! Adventure, fun, inspiration, and tips — you'll find it all here.

#AileenInItaly #Rome #ThroughEternityTours
